Author: DistractedBones
Text: I do a omad of 500 cal and I do feel guilty eating but I know that if I fast it increases my chances of a binge. I find that allowing myself to eat that much also helps the food thoughts as I know at the end of the day I'll get to eat.  It's totally unsustainable but the binge restrict cycle is horrible so this is better for now.
